# Media Standards

## Images

Always use:

Next Image

Requirements:

- blur placeholders
- proper sizes
- priority for hero

Prevent CLS.

## Photography

Only editorial quality imagery.

Never use generic stock photos.

## Video

Background videos:

muted
loop
playsInline
autoPlay

Use:

WebM
MP4 fallback

## Testimonial Videos

Never preload all videos.

Use:

preload="metadata"

Lazy load.

Mount only active video.

Pause hidden videos.
